  SFichier fic(fichier);

  fic << debut_phase << finl;
  fic << ind_phase << finl;
  fic << NN << finl;
  fic << Nv << finl;
  fic << Np << finl;

  for (int k=0; k<Np; k++)
    fic <<Nb_ech_phase(k) << finl;

    for (int j=0; j<Nv; j++)
      for (int i=0; i<NN; i++)
        fic << val(i,j,k) << finl;
}
